		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn-back {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.45rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		text-decoration: none;
